## 数据持久化策略

### Room 数据库设计

**表结构**
```sql
CREATE TABLE focus_strategies (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
    name TEXT NOT NULL,
    startHour INTEGER NOT NULL,
    startMinute INTEGER NOT NULL,
    endHour INTEGER NOT NULL,
    endMinute INTEGER NOT NULL,
    blockedPackages TEXT NOT NULL,  -- JSON 数组
    isActive INTEGER NOT NULL,       -- 0 或 1
    createdAt INTEGER NOT NULL,
    updatedAt INTEGER NOT NULL
);
```

**索引优化**
```kotlin
@Entity(
    tableName = "focus_strategies",
    indices = [
        Index(value = ["isActive"]),
        Index(value = ["createdAt"])
    ]
)
```

### 数据迁移策略

```kotlin
val MIGRATION_1_2 = object : Migration(1, 2) {
    override fun migrate(database: SupportSQLiteDatabase) {
        // 添加新列
        database.execSQL("ALTER TABLE focus_strategies ADD COLUMN priority INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0")
    }
}
```

